# <type>(<scope>): <description>
#
# [optional body]
#
# [optional footer(s)]
#
# Types: feat, fix, chore, docs, ci, test, perf, style, refactor, build
# Scope: optional, e.g. (extract), (cli), (types)
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add WOFF2 browser support
#   fix(extract): handle empty ligature tables
#   chore: update dependencies
#   perf: cache compiled SVG template
#
# Breaking changes: add "!" after type/scope, e.g. feat!: remove Node 18 support
# Or add "BREAKING CHANGE: ..." in the footer
